  "text": "Traced xDS configuration update flow across three repos. (1) Proto contract (sg-evals/data-plane-api--84e84367): discovery.proto defines DiscoveryRequest/DiscoveryResponse messages; ads.proto defines AggregatedDiscoveryService with StreamAggregatedResources (SotW) and DeltaAggregatedResources (Delta) RPCs. (2) Go server (sg-evals/go-control-plane--71637ad6): server.go implements StreamAggregatedResources (line 189) as the ADS entry point, delegating to sotw/server.go StreamHandler which spawns a goroutine reading DiscoveryRequest from the stream and sends DiscoveryResponse from a cache. discovery.pb.go contains the generated Go types. (3) Envoy C++ client (sg-evals/envoy--v1.31.2): GrpcSubscriptionImpl (grpc_subscription_impl.h) is the per-resource subscription adapter. It wraps GrpcMuxImpl (SotW) or NewGrpcMuxImpl (Delta). The subscription factory (grpc_subscription_factory.cc) creates the appropriate mux. XdsResourcesDelegate (xds_resources_delegate.h) provides extension hooks for custom xDS fetch/load logic.",
